 data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/hkon9agroup/permalink/2959858797388498?sfns=1</a><br />\n<br />\n🔟 黑警對白衣人及市民差別<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/westerndistrict/permalink/10156091909035286?sfns=1人\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2Fwesterndistrict%2Fpermalink%2F10156091909035286%3Fsfns%3D1%E4%BA%BA&d=FZf2Eq7oNugCj0cVmX%2F%2FqW7D9zYHOB9IQ%2BPXuKXaEI4%3D&h=d7b4bf91\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/westerndistrict/permalink/10156091909035286?sfns=1人</a>"},{"pid":"2dbe9d2e7055623e855a3c72c1f8c5bca2f10a7c","tid":1345513,"uid":3241,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T02:19:24.000Z","msg":"以黑警對一般市民搜身搜袋做法<br />\n<br />\n對白衣共党民兵態度簡單好似朋友一樣"},{"pid":"da04c6c493517971a97ab469a3cf0b101a1f9649","tid":1345513,"uid":16676,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T02:19:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JRY7Gfh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJRY7Gfh.png&h=22e9726d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tKje5GX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtKje5GX.png&h=d0a8df42&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n林鄭龜縮,政府唔回應市民後果<br />\n今日香港既局勢<br />\n完全係林鄭一手做成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59bee26290e280e50dee951f3c772069c1ad8667","tid":1345513,"uid":228793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T02:21:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dnvBzBG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdnvBzBG.jpg&h=43de131a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3ZVYNWG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3ZVYNWG.jpg&h=d47148f5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2def7b402a73e4388ed332e3cdfd199a0cfdde16","tid":1345513,"uid":61257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB